description: Are you looking for ridiculously amazing local Austin seafood, but don't have time to run to South Padre? Then head over to Fishey Bizness Seafood Co.! Thse unique flavors are primarily brought to you via local Texas seafood vendors, made by the hand of 'The Master' and owner Dennis White.The current menu primarily consists of fried shrimp, fried fish fillets, fish tacos and a healthy sized portion of fries on the side if you see fit. Needless to say, this seafood shack is not for the faint of heart!Come on out and enjoy a little piece of the south Texas beaches, a little closer to the ATX!
name: Fishey Bizness
